      "description": "This car is in fair condition. The exterior shows noticeable wear including minor dents and some surface rust in areas. The interior has visible wear on the upholstery and trim, with some components showing age. Mechanically, the car runs but has some issues that may require attention. Suitable for a buyer comfortable with a vehicle needing some work or maintenance.",
